snippet.title: Ominous Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist Now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2530970/Ominous/
Ominous is a thriller/horror game for up to 4 players. In this game, you must collaborate with your teammates to face a creature within an indoor setting. What sets Ominous apart is its unique approach to multiplayer, offering a distinct experience compared to many other horror games available.
